  <description>
    <p>
      Roll 'm Up is professional classic pinball game from late 90s with
      great graphics and music. Supports multi player game up to four players.
      The game has been created by Lostboys Media Lab for Dommelsch Brewery
      from Netherlands in 1998 as part of its marketing strategy. 
    </p>
    <p>
      Use Escape button in the game to open its main menu.
    </p>
    <p>
      This is abandoned proprietary software. Resizing window sometimes may 
      cause the game to crash. Take a look at README for other known issues:
      https://github.com/flathub/nl.lostboys.rollemup#known-issues
    </p>
  </description>
